@datapythonista @TomAugspurger 
Moto is supporting python 3.7. starting with 1.3.7 (the latest version), but that isn't reflected in the requirements yet: spulec/moto#1886

It's possible to install it through pip - I did that in #23731, but then the problem is that `1.3.7` requires a boto version that will run into #23754, probably because of a moto issue: spulec/moto#1941
